    <briefdescription>
<para>Flash storage port interface — implement these for your platform. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Used by the parameter store module for wear-leveled persistent storage. The port exposes raw sector-level operations; SyntropicOS handles wear leveling. </para>
